Install pip: 
Step1: Paste this in cmd  "curl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py -o get-pip.py"
Step2: Type python get-pip.py
Step3: Copy path C:\Users\godsu\AppData\Local\Programs\Python\Python312\Scripts
Step4: Open System Enviroment in Desktop
Step5: CLick on "Enviroment Variables.." option.
Step6: Now add path is "system variable"
Step7: CLick on "path" and click edit
Step8: CLick on "New"
Step9: Paste "Script Path" like step3.
Step10: Save and Done Error Fixed



Sucessfully Pip module installed as script file.
